‘findmnt’

Emacs hints: Help 'Back' button is 'l'. C-s C-w. C-g o. C-s g M-n. M-h.
Org mode: C-c C-o open link.
In git blame with ‘tig’: ‘%’ expands diff to all the files in the commit.
In fzf file search, to create new file (name already typed): C-x C-b name M-RET
In zsh, most recently edited file: C-x m

git

Fetch a pull request: ,github-pr [N]

